6. Transition Witness

Each state change produces a verifiable transition hash.

function transitionWitness(previousStateHash: string, operationHash: string, nextStateHash: string): string {
  return H(canonicalize({
    previous_state_hash: previousStateHash,
    operation_hash: operationHash,
    next_state_hash: nextStateHash
  }));
}

Purpose

preserve traceability

link consecutive states

avoid execution ambiguity

enable session reconstruction



